<div class="container-fluid d-flex flex-column justify-content-center align-items-center text-white mb-4">
    <div class="text-center mb-4">
        <h1>Contactez-nous</h1>
        <p class="m-0">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Nostrum facere autem
            provident, quibusdam ullam deserunt quos obcaecati incidunt praesentium sunt totam sed recusandae omnis
